Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我30分钟后要回去巡逻 有话快说 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm back on patrol in 30 minutes. So, talk fast. What happened?
