Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可我想听你亲口说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, I wanna hear it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一个孩子那里买大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was buying pot from this other kid.
