Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在干什么  - 搬进车库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The hell are you doing? - Moving into the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想 艾莉 放手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hell you are. Ellie, let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.47,0:26:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是半夜 外面下着大雨 把这个放回床上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the middle of the night. It's pissin' rain out there. Now, get this back on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.93,0:26:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,车库里没有暖气和自来水 你不能住进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no heat or running water in the garage. You can't stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.64,0:26:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你非要跟我说清楚 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you want to have this conversation? Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.48,0:26:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能不喜欢这里的规矩 但这是我家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may not like the rules, but this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.65,0:26:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是 你不是这里的主人 这是他们给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it isn't. You don't own it. They gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.48,0:26:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是给我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:26:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't own anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我纹了纹身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm sorry that I got a tattoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.17,0:27:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,抽了大麻 还和一个女孩鬼混\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and smoked weed, and fooled around with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.38,0:27:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过 我的道歉是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.76,0:27:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.18,0:27:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该有自己的空间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's a good thing for you to have your own space.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.98,0:27:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,给我几天时间修缮一下车库吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give me a few days and let me fix things up a little out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.61,0:27:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.41,0:27:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.42,0:28:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.55,0:28:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.97,0:28:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.56,0:28:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 疼吗  - 疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did it hurt? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是挺好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But kinda good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.28,0:28:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确实还不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's actually not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,至少比我在你吉他上刻的那个好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better than the one I made on your guitar anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.38,0:28:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没问过 你为什么喜欢飞蛾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never did ask. What is it with the moths?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.34,0:28:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. Just--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.84,0:28:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一本关于梦境的书里看到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just read about them in a book on dreams and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.35,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有点象征意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's kind of symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.97,0:28:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.31,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它代表改变和...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, like change and growin' and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成长之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.32,0:29:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.19,0:29:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.99,0:29:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.92,0:29:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(“大地永存”)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.51,0:29:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.18,0:29:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们研究梦境什么的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You guys study dreams and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.15,0:29:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上有“医生在此”的标志吗  就像“花生”漫画里的露西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a "Doctor Is In" sign on me like Lucy from fuckin' Peanuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.44,0:29:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 有些医生研究梦境 但大多是蠢医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, some doctors studied dreams. The dumb ones, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.74,0:29:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,飞蛾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, a moth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可能意味着改变和成长吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That probably means change and growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.91,0:29:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那是蝴蝶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that would be a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那飞蛾代表什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's a moth?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.92,0:30:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.34,0:30:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你相信那鬼东西的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you believe in that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.72,0:30:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.12,0:30:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(赞菲尔 “孤独的牧羊人”)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.02,0:31:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,(你有更伟大的使命)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.70,0:31:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(两年后)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这段时间 我一直在思考...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so I've been thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.50,0:31:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或者好奇 不 是思考\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or wondering-- no, thinking for a while now
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.05,0:31:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,盐湖城的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about Salt Lake City.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.01,0:31:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想弄明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.81,0:31:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我罗列了一些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I wrote down some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.89,0:31:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.23,0:31:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.11,0:31:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,“第一”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.91,0:31:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果火萤在离医院一英里的地方 发现了我们”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if the Fireflies spotted us a mile from the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.45,0:32:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,“他们怎么会 被一整群掠夺者突袭 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how did they get surprised by an entire group of Raiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.29,0:32:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“第二”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果掠夺者有本事 杀死所有士兵和玛琳”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Raiders could kill all those soldiers, and Marlene, 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.88,0:32:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,“而你一直背着我 我们是怎么逃出来的 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you had to carry me the whole time, how did we get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.72,0:32:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“第三”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three, 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.85,0:32:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果有几十个免疫者 为什么没人听说...”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if there are dozens of immune people, why hasn't anyone heard--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.98,0:32:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经穿好衣服了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Already dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我会吵醒你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figured I'd be waking you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我睡不着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope. I had trouble sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.75,0:32:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  这作为你的生日礼物再合适不过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, guess what? That works out great for your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.92,0:32:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你19岁了 一直很有耐心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're 19 and you've been patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.46,0:32:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我告诉他们我同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I told 'em I was okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.34,0:32:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,同意什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你第一次巡逻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your first patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去拿外套 - 还有枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll grab my coat. - And a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,实习巡逻的击杀纪录是多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's the record for number of kills on a training run?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.61,0:33:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,零 这是目前最安全的路径 得从简单的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zero. This is the safest trail we got. Gotta start easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 祝我生日快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. Happy birthday to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.91,0:33:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把望远镜拿出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, binoculars. 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.45,0:33:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 这里什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? There's nothing out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但这是为了熟悉流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, but this is about learnin' the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.13,0:33:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,假装一下 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, pretend, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.30,0:33:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是规定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's part of the rules. 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.63,0:33:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟紧你的搭档 搜索郊区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stick with your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,随时做好一切准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}scan the countryside, be ready for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.09,0:33:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死  - 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, shit. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有只小松鼠在操一只大松鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a little squirrel fucking a big squirrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.73,0:33:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也许应该汇报上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should probably report that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.52,0:33:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 暂时不要搜索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine, we'll skip the scannin' for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.90,0:33:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉挺好的 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.99,0:33:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了以前 只有咱俩在林间的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reminds me of the old days, just you and me on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.91,0:34:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你有事要忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you got stuff going on, but it'd be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.41,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要是能经常这样就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we could do this kind of thing more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.58,0:34:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多花点时间相处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spend time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.17,0:34:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.80,0:34:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可你看起来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just, you look... 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我只是... - 你没心事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, I-- - There's nothin' on your mind? 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.60,0:34:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 - “卡什溪 这里是杰克逊”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, nothing. - Cache Creek, this is Jackson. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.77,0:34:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是卡什溪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go for Cache Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.23,0:34:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“顶峰以北发现感染者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Infected north of Pinnacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.81,0:34:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“尤金和亚当需要支援 你们离那里最近”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eugene and Adam need backup. You're the closest we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我十分钟后到 叫他们开始行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be there in ten. Tell them to dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回杰克逊 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go back to Jackson. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.74,0:34:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 这里不安全 快回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie, it's not safe. Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.45,0:34:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子 乔尔 我是你的搭档 我们不能分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not your fucking kid, Joel. I'm your partner. We stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.79,0:34:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.32,0:35:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从这里走下去 比走弯道还快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll hike down from here. Faster than the switchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.48,0:35:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,记得我教你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember what I taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.19,0:35:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互为后盾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm your back. You're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.65,0:36:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit. Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.26,0:37:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你被咬了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.57,0:37:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.07,0:37:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有感染者吗  - 乔尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are there any more? - Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有感染者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are there any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.95,0:37:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other than me?
