Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.47,0:53:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道迪娜的心意 但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I don't know what Dina's intentions are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.19,0:53:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她能拥有你是她的幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, she'd be lucky to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.48,0:53:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're such an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.66,0:53:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.66,0:53:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼睁睁地骗了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You looked me in the eyes and you lied, 
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.29,0:53:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候也是这张脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it was the same face.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.29,0:53:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Same fucking look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.17,0:53:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我早就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think I knew already.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.39,0:53:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.64,0:53:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我再给你最后一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I'm gonna give you one last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.86,0:54:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我火萤到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what happened with the Fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.49,0:54:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再骗我 我们就别来往了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you lie to me again, we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.46,0:54:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真有其他免疫者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were there other immune people?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.85,0:54:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的遇到了掠夺者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were there Raiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.99,0:54:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能研制出解药吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could they have made a cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.30,0:55:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.18,0:55:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,包括玛琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Marlene?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.90,0:55:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,研制解药...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Making a cure
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.20,0:55:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,会要了你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would've killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.28,0:55:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就该死 那是我的使命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, I was supposed to die. That was my purpose. 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.70,0:55:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的命本来很重要 但你剥夺了我的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My life would have fucking mattered! But you took that from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.79,0:55:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你剥夺了所有人的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You took it from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.59,0:55:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.76,0:55:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会付出代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll pay the price
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.89,0:55:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会背弃我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you're gonna turn away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.02,0:56:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果让我重来一遍...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if somehow I had a second chance at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.86,0:56:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是会那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would do it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.61,0:56:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你很自私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.91,0:56:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.67,0:56:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,以一种...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.46,0:56:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法理解的方式爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.67,0:56:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你永远理解不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.51,0:56:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果将来有一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if that day should come,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.97,0:56:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你有了自己的孩子...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you should ever have one of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.69,0:56:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.95,0:56:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你做得比我稍好一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you do a little better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.43,0:57:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我没办法原谅你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think I can forgive you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.52,0:57:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我愿意试试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would like to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.69,0:58:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.69,0:58:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏
